  "texts": [
    "Expert oversight remains essential for ensuring patient safety and a nuanced understanding of clinical context.",
    "Practical considerations such as availability of funding, ease of patient recruitment and alternative trial designs such as open-label, cross-over or pragmatic trials were not considered in this study.",
    "General-purpose LLM used in our study is also limited by lack of knowledge on unpublished data from in-house experiments, an important consideration in clinical trial design.",
    "Furthermore, careful regulatory measures are required to ensure the safety, privacy, and ethical conduct of RCTs.",
    "We randomly selected 10 published RCTs across various medical specialties, published in leading clinical journals, and 10 ongoing registered RCTs listed on ClinicalTrial.gov."
